title: d.j.v. beautenizer d.j.v. beautenizer Fiberwig LX Pure Black
description: What it is:A false lash formula that's applied like mascara and encapsulates lashes within a fiber-rich film.What it does:This glossy, black formula contains double the fibers to lengthen lashes. As the formula goes on smoothly without clumping, it gives the appearance of naturally longer lashes and forms a film coating that prevents smudging caused by oils and perspiration. The active ingredients consist of several natural botanical essences, a silky fiber ingredient, and panthenol to help nourish and strengthen lashes.What it is formulated WITHOUT:- Sulfates- Synthetic Fragrances- Synthetic Dyes- Phthalates- TriclosanWhat else you need to know:Easy removal with warm water, which loosens the film and allows the formula to slide off easily.
